items.sentence: Tom knows that Mary can't speak French very well.
Tom said that you're better at French than he is.
Do you remember the first time you talked to Tom?
I didn't think that we could do anything for Tom.
I didn't think that anybody could've stopped Tom.
I didn't think anybody suspected you weren't Tom.
I've seen you before, but I can't remember where.
I'm not positive this is what we should be doing.
Do you know how to make Thousand Island dressing?
Tom gave a disarming smile and continued talking.
